-- Citigroup Sued by Swisscanto Over Comments About Mortgage Loans
-- B y   D a v i d   G l o v i n
-- 2012-12-12T21:36:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-12/citigroup-sued-by-swisscanto-over-comments-about-mortgage-loans.html
Citigroup Inc. (C)  was accused in a
lawsuit by Swisscanto Asset Management AG of making misleading
statements about its financial condition from 2006 to 2009.  The suit in Manhattan federal court focuses on statements
the New York-based bank made about the risks it faced over
mortgage loans.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Glovin in New York at 
 dglovin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Dunn at 
